Dialogue: 0,1:53:51.76,1:53:53.40,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\NSo did I.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.44,1:53:54.92,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  你赢了\NYes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.28,1:53:59.52,BLC-50,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺你的成功  这是你应得的\NCongratulations on your success. You deserve it.
